title: J&K: Encounter underway between security forces, terrorists in Bandipora, 4 jawans injured
text:
J&K: Encounter underway between security forces, terrorists in Bandipora, 4 jawans injured J&K: Encounter underway between security forces, terrorists in Bandipora, 4 jawans injured Four jawans have been injured in the encounter. By: Express Web Desk | New Delhi | Updated: February 14, 2017 7:34 am 
An encounter is underway between security forces and terrorists in Hajin area of Bandipora district in Jammu & Kashmir. As per the preliminary reports, four jawans have beem injured. More details awaited. © The Indian Express Online Media Pvt Ltd
